}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== Resetting the device to factory defaults via the reset button or web configration interface sets the SSID to '''Belkin_G_Plus_MIMO_180170''' (even though the SSID in the SSID field on the web configration interface says '''Belkin_G_Plus_MIMO_XXXXXX''' [where '''XXXXXX''' is the last three octets of the wireless interface MAC w/ upper case letters]). The SSID setting fresh from the factory is unknown.
